Package com.vmware.appliance.vcenter.settings.v1.config.components.inventory.cluster.drs

The com.vmware.appliance.vcenter.settings.v1.config.components.inventory.cluster.drs package provides interfaces to manage the vCenter Server Inventory Cluster DRS settings.

Package com.vmware.appliance.vcenter.settings.v1.config.components.inventory.cluster.drs Description

The com.vmware.appliance.vcenter.settings.v1.config.components.inventory.cluster.drs package provides interfaces to manage the vCenter Server Inventory Cluster DRS settings.
